@{
    ViewBag.Title = "ASP.NET MVC Boilerplate";
    ViewBag.Description = "A professional ASP.NET MVC template for building secure, fast, robust and adaptable web applications or sites. It provides the minimum amount of code required on top of the default MVC template provided by Microsoft.";
}

<header class="jumbotron">
    <h1>@ViewBag.Title</h1>
    <p class="lead">@ViewBag.Description</p>
    <p><a href="https://github.com/RehanSaeed/ASP.NET-MVC-Boilerplate" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Learn more &raquo;</a></p>
</header>

<div class="row">
    <article class="col-md-4">
        <header>
            <h2>Getting started</h2>
        </header>
        <p>
            ASP.NET Web API is a framework that makes it easy to build HTTP services that reach
            a broad range of clients, including browsers and mobile devices. ASP.NET Web API
            is an ideal platform for building RESTful applications on the .NET Framework.
        </p>
        <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=301870">Learn more &raquo;</a></p>
    </article>
    <article class="col-md-4">
        <header>
            <h2>Get more libraries</h2>
        </header>
        <p>NuGet is a free Visual Studio extension that makes it easy to add, remove, and update libraries and tools in Visual Studio projects.</p>
        <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=301871">Learn more &raquo;</a></p>
    </article>
    <article class="col-md-4">
        <header>
            <h2>Web Hosting</h2>
        </header>
        <p>You can easily find a web hosting company that offers the right mix of features and price for your applications.</p>
        <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=301872">Learn more &raquo;</a></p>
    </article>
</div>

<div class="row">
    <article class="col-md-4">
        <header>
            <h2>Bootstrap</h2>
        </header>
        <p>Bootstrap is the most popular HTML, CSS, and JS framework for developing responsive, mobile first projects on the web.</p>
        <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="http://getbootstrap.com/getting-started/">Learn more &raquo;</a></p>
    </article>
    <article class="col-md-4">
        <header>
            <h2>Font Awesome</h2>
        </header>
        <p>Font Awesome gives you scalable vector icons that can instantly be customized — size, color, drop shadow, and anything that can be done with the power of CSS.</p>
        <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="http://fortawesome.github.io/Font-Awesome/">Learn more &raquo;</a></p>
    </article>
    <article class="col-md-4">
        <header>
            <h2>Modernizr</h2>
        </header>
        <p>Modernizr is a JavaScript library that detects HTML5 and CSS3 features in the user’s browser.</p>
        <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="http://modernizr.com/">Learn more &raquo;</a></p>
    </article>
</div>

<div class="row">
    <article class="col-md-4">
        <header>
            <h2>NWebsec</h2>
        </header>
        <p>NWebsec makes securing your ASP.NET MVC site easy with a handful of simple attributes you can add to your global filters, controllers or actions.</p>
        <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="https://nwebsec.codeplex.com/wikipage?title=NWebsec.Mvc&referringTitle=Documentation">Learn more &raquo;</a></p>
    </article>
    <article class="col-md-4">
        <header>
            <h2>Elmah</h2>
        </header>
        <p>ELMAH (Error Logging Modules and Handlers) is an application-wide error logging facility that is completely pluggable.</p>
        <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="https://code.google.com/p/elmah/wiki/MVC">Learn more &raquo;</a></p>
    </article>
    <article class="col-md-4">
        <header>
            <h2>Glimpse</h2>
        </header>
        <p>Makes debugging and performance testing easier by providing real time diagnostics & insights.</p>
        <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="http://getglimpse.com/">Learn more &raquo;</a></p>
    </article>
</div>

<div class="row">
    <article class="col-md-4">
        <header>
            <h2>Autofac</h2>
        </header>
        <p>Autofac is an addictive <a href="http://martinfowler.com/articles/injection.html">inversion of control</a> container.</p>
        <p><a class="btn btn-default" href="http://autofac.org/">Learn more &raquo;</a></p>
    </article>
</div>